}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "20081107" and "AWR2114gA" is silkscrened on one production unit's board. :The second LAN port is covered by tape on the unit's shell.
The manufacturer of this device is likely the same as that of the [[RadioLabs AWR1114gA]]. .. probably '''ARGtek'''.
The PoE voltage is '''''assumed''''' to be 48V, per [http://www.premiertek.net/products/networking/GS-CPE3014-1W.html this '''Premiertek''' product page].
